snippet.textOriginal: The music is as good as it always has been on Coke Studio but I think we will remember this season more for creating some of the most beautiful sets to represent different cultures and their people.

snippet.textDisplay: @Coke studio, Kudos to everyone involved. You guys are doing a phenomenal job introducing the world to this wonderful side of Pakistan, making each and everyone of us so proud. While season 14 was amazing but for me, this season has just gone to another level. Introducing Pakistani culture and languages in a modern manner has touched the right cords of my heart and I am so very sure many others feel the same way. Keep rocking and continue to produce the wonderful work that you guys are known for. We are so lucky to have Coke Studio Pakistan that make us all so proud!
